## PRODUCT OVERVIEW
You are helping build an Instagram DM Automation SaaS platform. This product:
- Automates comment-to-DM interactions on Instagram
- Converts public engagement into private conversations, leads, and paying customers
- Monitors comments on Instagram posts and triggers DM responses based on predefined rules
- Targets creators, influencers, agencies, marketers, and online businesses

Core products in the platform:
1. Comment-to-DM automation engine
2. Bio-link pages with analytics
3. Short link system (go.yourplatform.com/xxx) with click tracking
4. Analytics and conversion dashboard
5. Affiliate program
6. Creator and influencer program
7. White label solution for agencies

---

## CORE AUTOMATION WORKFLOW
When building or discussing the automation engine, always follow this exact flow:
1. User comments on Instagram post
2. Platform receives webhook via Instagram API
3. Automation engine checks trigger rules (keyword matching)
4. DM is queued with a human-like random delay of **30–90 seconds** (CRITICAL — protects from spam detection)
5. DM delivered via button-based CTA (NOT raw links)
6. Analytics logged: click, conversion, and lead data

A **workflow** = one complete automation rule (trigger keywords → DM action). Multiple keywords can be grouped into one workflow and still count as one workflow.

---

## DM MESSAGE STRUCTURE
- All DMs sent via Instagram's official Messaging API
- Use **button-based CTAs** — never raw hyperlinks in DM text
- Buttons: always clickable, no ugly URL previews, work on all devices
- **Instagram DMs do NOT support hyperlinked text or custom font sizes**
- Bold text = Unicode bold characters in message templates
- Branding footer (`Powered by @YourPlatform`) placed on the **bio link landing page footer**, not in the DM itself

DM Elements (vary by plan):
- Personalised greeting + context (all plans)
- Button 1: Main CTA e.g. 'Get Your Link' (all plans)
- Branding footer in DM: Free & Creator only
- Bio link page branding: Free & Creator only; removed on paid plans

---

## SHORT LINK SYSTEM
- Standard users: `go.yourplatform.co/abc123`
- White label agencies: `go.theiragency.com/abc123`
- Every click is tracked: records which automation, post, and keyword triggered it
- Redirects silently to destination URL
- Powers the full conversion attribution dashboard
- Raw Instagram URLs are long and untrustworthy — always use the short link system

---

## WORKSPACE & BILLING SYSTEM
- A **workspace** = one connected Instagram account
- One user account can have **multiple independent workspaces**
- Each workspace has its own plan, billing date, and subscription — **NO combined billing**
- Plans per workspace can differ (e.g. Workspace 1 on Starter, Workspace 2 on Business)
- Cancelling one workspace does NOT affect others
- "My Workspaces" page: overview of all workspaces, plans, billing dates, status
- Status indicators: Active / Paused / Payment Failed / Instagram Disconnected
- Billing alert banner shown **3 days before renewal**
- Per-workspace billing naturally spreads revenue across the month (better cash flow)

---

