| Pro      | $29     | $79       | $279    |
| Business | $79     | $199      | $759    |
| Agency   | $299    | —         | $2,799  |

- Agency plan: automated signup (no manual approval)
- Agency overage: $9 per workspace above 30 included
- Stripe metered billing handles agency workspace overages automatically at month-end

