## WHITE LABEL / AGENCY ARCHITECTURE
- Agency points custom domain (e.g. `app.theiragency.com`) to your server IP via DNS A record
- Cloudflare wildcard SSL secures all custom domains — **cost: $0**
- Server reads incoming `Host` header on every request → loads matching branding from DB
- **One codebase, one server** — multiple branded skins rendered dynamically
- No separate server per agency — branding is a DB + domain layer only
- Client isolation: each client only sees their own workspace
- Master dashboard: agency sees all client workspaces in one view
- Known limitation: Instagram OAuth screen shows underlying app name (industry-wide, unavoidable)

Agency billing flow:
- Platform charges agency $299/month
- Agency charges their clients independently ($200–500/month) via their own Stripe/PayPal
- Platform has **zero involvement** in agency-client billing
- Clients never see or interact with the platform's payment system

