## BIO LINK PRODUCT
- Serves as standalone tool AND primary viral growth funnel
- Free users: bio link page with platform branding in footer
- Paid users: branding removed

Features:
- Profile photo, name, short bio
- Customisable links and buttons (plan-based limits)
- Product, offer, lead magnet buttons
- Contact CTA buttons
- Theme colors, button styles, light/dark mode, custom icons

Analytics:
- Total page views & unique visitors
- Total link clicks + per-link clicks
- Automation-driven conversion tracking
- Daily, weekly, monthly insights

