## ANALYTICS & CONVERSION TRACKING
Full conversion attribution: comment → DM → click → sale (via short link + UTM params).
This is a key differentiator vs competitors who only show DM volume.

| Metric                    | Plan        |
|---------------------------|-------------|
| DMs sent/failed/queued    | All         |
| Automation performance    | All         |
| Post-level breakdown      | Standard+   |
| Keyword conversion rate   | Advanced    |
| Link click tracking       | Advanced    |
| Sale attribution          | Advanced    |
| Automation ROI            | Advanced    |

