## PAYMENT GATEWAYS
- **Stripe**: International — Cards, Apple Pay, Google Pay. Handles subscriptions + metered agency billing.
- **Razorpay**: India only — UPI, Cards, Netbanking. Faster payouts for Indian users.
- Use Stripe metered billing for the $9/workspace overage on Agency plan (charged at month-end).

---

## CREATOR / INFLUENCER PROGRAM
- Free Business-level access to selected creators
- Max 50 creators at initial launch
- Requirements: minimum 300 DMs/month + 2 active automation campaigns per 30 days
- Auto-alert sent on Day 25 if creator is below 300 DM threshold
- Branding: `Powered by @YourPlatform` footer on bio link page only
- Creators are NOT paid sales — they are an organic acquisition channel

Green flag creators: >3% engagement rate, 5k–100k followers, post weekly, niche-aligned (business/marketing/creator/fitness)
Red flag creators: high follower + low engagement, generic bot-like comments, irregular posting, promoting competing tools

---

## AFFILIATE PROGRAM
- Eligible: ALL users including Free plan
- Commission: 25% one-time per referred sale (NOT recurring — protects cash flow)
- Minimum payout: $25
- Approval delay: 14–30 days (fraud buffer)
- Eligible plans: Starter, Pro, Business, Agency
- Self-referrals: strictly prohibited → account suspension
- Affiliate links: manually shared only, NEVER auto-inserted into automation messages

